  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Output 2: Supporting knowledge exchange and innovative climate smart and gender sensitive initiatives, to build decentralised systems that are responsive to the needs of the furthest behind, thereby reducing humanitarian need and building resilience.</narrative>
